:Dimorphic_hemorrhoidspiles :description "Hemorrhoids, also spelled haemorrhoids, are vascular structures in the anal canal. In their ... Other names, Haemorrhoids, piles, hemorrhoidal disease ." .

:Drug_Reaction a :Disease ;
    :description "An adverse drug reaction (ADR) is an injury caused by taking medication. ADRs may occur following a single dose or prolonged administration of a drug or result from the combination of two or more drugs." ;
    :hasSymptom :burning_micturition,
        :itching,
        :skin_rash,
        :spotting_urination,
        :stomach_pain ;
    :hasTreatment :ConsultNearestHospital,
